## DAY 3 — Reddit Posts

These drive real traffic fast:

Post in these subreddits one by one (don't spam — be genuine):

- **r/SEO** → "I built a free keyword research tool with no daily limits — feedback welcome"
- **r/Blogging** → "Free tool I made for keyword research — no sign up needed"
- **r/juststart** → Share your story
- **r/indiebusiness** → "Built this for free as a side project"

**Rule:** Don't just drop a link. Write 3-4 sentences about WHY you built it and what problem it solves. Then mention the link at the end.

